[{"client_msg_id":"6ebd841f-0234-41ea-ac91-649b9dba6615","type":"message","user":"UAZ33BKV2","text":"全国の求職者の内、デジタル庁への希望者が募集の何倍いるか、どれだけの人気なのか、につかう値ってところかな\nこの倍率表記とか、それをこの記事が採用したことが、正解かはまた別...かな(適切とはちょっと思えない部分もあるし)","ts":"1611712639.251300","team":"T03C4RC8V","reactions":[{"name":"naruhodo","count":1,"users":["U01EMNN9XNG"]}],"replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"HqPw"}]},{"client_msg_id":"778ca1cb-3596-4690-bc55-fbbfd7e9dfbb","type":"message","user":"U01EMNN9XNG","text":"• デジタル庁に就職の希望者（募集人数） = 1432人\n• 日本国に新しい職に付きたい人＝300万人 （推定）\n• 募集人数 ÷ 求職者 = 0.0004773\nで合ってます？全国の求職者に対しての倍率を示したい場合記事に使われるのかな？","ts":"1611712473.249300","edited":{"user":"U01EMNN9XNG","ts":"1611712483.000000"},"team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"oLs"}]},{"client_msg_id":"fe3fb164-7ab6-4021-b431-4766c753e745","type":"message","user":"UGXMRNBUM","text":"具体的な一企業への希望者（＝募集）ではなく、一般に職に付きたい人（求職者）という表現です","ts":"1611711504.244800","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"EHFUL"}]},{"client_msg_id":"4eb09fe3-eee0-4e47-8c52-345e404799fd","type":"message","user":"UGXMRNBUM","text":"そちらは逆に、例えばある大学の学生を求めて「1人の学生に対して20社が声をかけてる」状態を指して、\n求人倍率20倍、なんて言って会社側の競争率の高さを表現したりしますね。\n\nこの時、今年度の卒業生のうち就職志望の者を指して「求職者」と表現したりします。","ts":"1611711419.243500","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"pLHO"}]},{"client_msg_id":"c19e85e9-cc3f-4d56-bac6-e52e152b70ca","type":"message","user":"U01EMNN9XNG","text":"うん。。。","ts":"1611711374.242600","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"u15FC"}]},{"client_msg_id":"f69257e3-42b8-43fe-9212-33fd3a66a27e","type":"message","user":"U01EMNN9XNG","text":"求職の人は募集するので？","ts":"1611711364.242300","edited":{"user":"U01EMNN9XNG","ts":"1611711421.000000"},"team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"6DHOX"}]},{"client_msg_id":"af6bce52-1039-49e9-9e77-4c0d33959b6a","type":"message","user":"U01EMNN9XNG","text":"\u0026gt; よく似た求人倍率の文脈だと募集人数 ÷ 求職者だからややこしいな\n募集人数と求職者どう違いますか？","ts":"1611711346.241400","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"LUwX"}]},{"client_msg_id":"051948e7-5b4a-4872-8dd9-3c3197a72eb0","type":"message","user":"UAZ33BKV2","text":"1つの席に47人応募がある率だ、ということですね(取る側からみた感じになるな)","ts":"1611711199.239200","team":"T03C4RC8V","reactions":[{"name":"naruhodo","count":1,"users":["U01EMNN9XNG"]}],"replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"XnYIA"}]},{"client_msg_id":"51144a17-439b-4363-b455-cc19b4d4fe12","type":"message","user":"U01EMNN9XNG","text":"偏差値と同じように","ts":"1611711191.239000","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"sZ7"}]},{"client_msg_id":"176d809b-a689-49f7-894d-eda4d2402a1c","type":"message","user":"UGXMRNBUM","text":"（今回のような）採用の文脈では応募人数 ÷ 募集人数だし、\nよく似た求人倍率の文脈だと募集人数 ÷ 求職者だからややこしいな","ts":"1611711189.238900","team":"T03C4RC8V","reactions":[{"name":"naruhodo","count":1,"users":["U01EMNN9XNG"]}],"replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"/xi"}]},{"client_msg_id":"63527a0d-4103-4355-abd8-9ad6a5d3c3f8","type":"message","user":"U01EMNN9XNG","text":"これ英語圏じゃ使われないと思う","ts":"1611711185.238500","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"SEbU"}]},{"client_msg_id":"b3dbfbab-c2b9-4831-aec0-83b283960dab","type":"message","user":"U01EMNN9XNG","text":"なるほどぉ","ts":"1611711145.237300","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"MzJgd"}]},{"client_msg_id":"35b5ca35-85c2-46ed-81ab-da03703d9aa6","type":"message","user":"U01EMNN9XNG","tex