7倍に達する。」","ts":"1611710576.231300","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"aH4S"}]},{"client_msg_id":"1a95175a-9ffe-4387-baa1-6ebee73c490f","type":"message","user":"U01EMNN9XNG","text":"難しい記事ですね","ts":"1611710564.231000","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"/E="}]},{"client_msg_id":"364ccd5a-1e01-4177-b820-9ecccad78a33","type":"message","user":"U01EMNN9XNG","text":"From \u003c#C03C4RC9F|random\u003e: \u003chttps://news.yahoo.co.jp/articles/75b1deeff04669260d0009ef39c40bdab590837a\u003e","ts":"1611710559.230700","attachments":[{"fallback":"Yahoo!ニュース: デジタル庁先行採用、倍率47倍　民間人材枠、約30人を募集（共同通信） - Yahoo!ニュース","id":1,"title":"デジタル庁先行採用、倍率47倍　民間人材枠、約30人を募集（共同通信） - Yahoo!ニュース","title_link":"https://news.yahoo.co.jp/articles/75b1deeff04669260d0009ef39c40bdab590837a","text":"　平井卓也デジタル改革担当相は26日の閣議後記者会見で、9月のデジタル庁創設に向け先行募集した民間人材について、30人程度の採用枠に20～70代の1432人の応募があったと明らかにした。倍率は47.","image_url":"https://s.yimg.jp/images/jpnews/cre/common/all/images/fbico_ogp_1200x630.png","blocks":null,"service_name":"Yahoo!ニュース","service_icon":"https://s.yimg.jp/c/icon/s/bsc/2.0/news120.png","from_url":"https://news.yahoo.co.jp/articles/75b1deeff04669260d0009ef39c40bdab590837a","original_url":"https://news.yahoo.co.jp/articles/75b1deeff04669260d0009ef39c40bdab590837a"}],"team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"HKM"}]}]
